###############################
#  DNS Monitor                #
###############################

Written by: Napalm

Description:

  The tool runs in your Windows System Tray, monitoring website's DNS results.

  Monitor A and B side websites.

  Customize Foreground and Background Colors for matching results.

Syntax:

  DNS Servers:
	x.x.x.x, y.y.y.y, z.z.z.z

  Domain Names:
	sample.com, example.com

  DNS Matches:
	SIDEA:xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
	or
	SIDEA:xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx:(ffffff|000000)

	Note:(ffffff|000000) == (foreground|background)
	Note: Color is optional